    public class ConstrainedNumericTextTag
extends org.apache.struts.taglib.html.TextTag
    This example tag extends the Struts TextTag and adds a JavaScript handler for checking numeric constraints. Have a look at ConstrainedNumericTextTagTest to see how to test simple tags.
